text:
Kim Kardashian and Jennifer Lawrence hilariously recalled what happened after J.Law had dinner with the famous reality clan during an appearance on Jimmy Kimmel Live! on Thursday, November 2.

Lawrence was filling in for Kimmel, who was with his family for his son’s surgery.

“It was everything I could have ever dreamed of,” Lawrence gushed of getting to meet the Kardashians.
title: Kim K.: J. Law Ended Up ‘Fully Butt Naked’ In Kris Jenner’s Closet
